<h2 id="Kong启动"><a href="#Kong启动" class="headerlink" title="Kong启动"></a>Kong启动</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kong start -c &#x2F;etc&#x2F;kong&#x2F;kong.conf --v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

