<h2 id="Kong重载配置"><a href="#Kong重载配置" class="headerlink" title="Kong重载配置"></a>Kong重载配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kong reload -c &#x2F;etc&#x2F;kong&#x2F;kong.conf --v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>输出示例</p>
